{"tid":706984,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"顏值過低！連格拖累英格蘭7號進化史","createTime":"2018-06-18T10:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T20:53:40.000Z","uid":34572,"like":28,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"946c6b686ccc77401aa82c0f1296a84415f7004a","tid":706984,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"英格蘭喺「萬人迷」碧咸後，7號波衫繼承者愈搞愈冇星味，今次俄羅斯世盃連格得到7號球衣，更加因為輸在起跑線，顏值過低被封為英格蘭史上最弱雞7號，甚至有網友話，連格拖累英格蘭7號進化史添呀陰公！<br />\n<br />\n同曼聯一樣，英格蘭出過唔少經典7號，例如馬菲斯、基雲基瑾、白賴仁笠臣同碧咸，佢哋全部星味濃烈，點知碧咸淡出英格蘭國家隊後，7號繼承者變成艾朗連儂、禾確特、韋舒亞同史達寧，偶像味大減，今次輪到連格更加令到網友嗌救命。<br />\n<br />\n其實連格今季喺曼聯表現唔差，仲入過唔少靚波，可惜佢真係欠缺爆紅嘅先天條件，就係顏值不足，球迷唔止冷落佢，仲笑佢係英格蘭史上最弱雞7號，拎佢同碧咸比簡直係得啖笑，唯有希望連格喺俄羅斯踢好波，證明自己襯得起件波衫啦！"},{"pid":"f60bb3def805dfab9c0038ffad1a8e91d4c9af23","tid":706984,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"俾連仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d540227a78ba6c5a7f5baa7b4e1e851f031c2236","tid":706984,"uid":132587,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"力架入侵左歐洲d國家之後隊隊都樣衰左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2367ae68f969c58b9cec11f0d346981dbe3728","tid":706984,"uid":31314,"like":136,"dislike":10,"score":126,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.cityam.com/assets/uploads/main-image/cam_standard_article_main_image/fbl-friendly-ned-eng-937115104-5b26c4d61c562.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cityam.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2Fmain-image%2Fcam_standard_article_main_image%2Ffbl-friendly-ned-eng-937115104-5b26c4d61c562.jpg&h=a283f92c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個弱智咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eecdd43e412471487c8c772d5b3802b61d3f5b8","tid":706984,"uid":4586,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"8e2367ae68f969c58b9cec11f0d346981dbe3728","tid":706984,"uid":31314,"like"